The article discusses the issue of fraudulent or meritless asylum claims being used as a loophole for illegal immigrants to enter the United States. President Donald J. Trump is described as taking steps to protect the integrity of the asylum system and address the humanitarian and security crisis at the border. It is stated that migrants are using asylum claims to gain entry into the country and stay indefinitely. The article also mentions the need to reduce asylum fraud by preventing illegal migrants with meritless claims from entering and remaining in the country.